    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MIMANIA</strong> is a survival horror game where your goal is to find all the mimics hidden in different locations. These mimics are disguised as ordinary furniture, so keep your eyes open for any strange behaviour.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although you may appear to be alone in a location, <strong>DO NOT</strong> let your guard down.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167930/extras/b2c01236e9001af5ec7a2703f8ed54b9.poster.avif?t=1771622995\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167930/extras/b2c01236e9001af5ec7a2703f8ed54b9.webm?t=1771622995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167930/extras/b2c01236e9001af5ec7a2703f8ed54b9.mp4?t=1771622995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167930/extras/e3b28caca0b7facc2fe9d549621d8ce0.webp?t=1771622995\" width=256 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your trusty camera's flash to defend yourself against  anything lurking inside the darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167930/extras/e2e1a7a7e1cb00adca563e0ba338ec4c.poster.avif?t=1771622995\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167930/extras/e2e1a7a7e1cb00adca563e0ba338ec4c.webm?t=1771622995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167930/extras/e2e1a7a7e1cb00adca563e0ba338ec4c.mp4?t=1771622995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167930/extras/57f72a8eab81addc7420f7be093b2bc2.webp?t=1771622995\" width=400 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>* Explore 5 unique environments</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>* Each environment has a unique monster</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>* Small mimics that are disguised as ordinary furniture</strong></p>",
